1. *Ideš* li u školu? (Are you going to school?)
2. On *ide* na kontrolu. (He is going for a check-up.)
3. Ona *ide* u šetnju. (She is going for a walk.)
4. *Ideš* li s nama? (Are you going with us?)
5. Mi *idemo* do sela. (We are going to the village.)
6. On *ide* u kino. (He is going to the cinema.)
7. *Ideš* li da se igraš? (Are you going to play?)
8. Mi *idemo* u kupovinu. (We are going shopping.)